content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 96.15 - Complying with federal and state seed laws

State Regulations

Responsibility for any obligations relating to proper
labeling of seed, other than those concerned with certification (e.g., proper
techniques in establishing genetic identity of seed), arising from the sale or
shipment of seed which has been certified, rests with the grower or subsequent
handler making the sale or shipment. Notes
